    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal lateral dynamics. Recent preventative maintenance includes the critical rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are robust. The chassis remains taut with the EDC (Electronic Damper Control) functioning correctly across all damping maps. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp. This is a slicktop specimen, offering maximum structural rigidity and a lower center of gravity for the discerning purist.",
