      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for 2016 Lexus GX 460 Luxury, finished in a timeless Starfire Pearl with a Parchment leather interior. This vehicle has been a reliable family companion and shows the pride of ownership. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather is soft and free of tears, though there is light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All power features, including the heated/ventilated seats, sunroof, and third-row power-folding seats, operate perfectly. Mechanically, this GX is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly at the dealership, with a recent 90,000-mile service already completed, including a coolant flush and new brake pads. The 4.6L V8 engine is smooth and powerful, and the 4WD system handles flawlessly. This is a solid, honest luxury SUV that bridges the gap between a showroom piece and a dependable daily driver.",
